{"tid":1143321,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"F.I.R 新專輯","createTime":"2019-05-07T15:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T00:49:37.000Z","uid":8996,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8534c04ddaa2ed23ce089d4d4085b3191656cc23","tid":1143321,"uid":8996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"末日青春: 補完計劃 <br />\n<br />\n第一波主打<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LeUMB8GXL7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLeUMB8GXL7k&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=67e87165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LeUMB8GXL7k</a><br />\n<br />\n第二波主打<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jU2FQfoTvEg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjU2FQfoTvEg&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=992b14b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jU2FQfoTvEg</a><br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3mEeKAdXAo4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3mEeKAdXAo4&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=3ac5cf87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3mEeKAdXAo4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1683fd5d983c4d978b92679306993d5c21cc354","tid":1143321,"uid":141589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi