,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"咁一個團入面三條友  走左Faye就要改名?<br />\n陳建寧同阿沁都係核心之一  其實樂團換下主唱,鼓手好正常<br />\n其次個團本身有返咁上下知名度, 改個名重新出發?<br />\n就算佢地肯 公司都未必肯啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"理論上係...但係問心<br />\n有啲隊係有靈魂人物既<br />\n簡單啲講<br />\n有家駒既beyond同無已經差好遠啦"},{"pid":"e33e3558d063e782eaac4473d84f6ded8bb75578","tid":1143321,"uid":88785,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91f552dc0c6f3f4f2fdbcf7e71fabc8ba6109616","tid":1143321,"uid":8996,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9396c3918dbc2ef14b53a13ee7fc31bc0613c1a","tid":1143321,"uid":60677,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"多年死忠表示無咗Faye真係無興趣聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"對事唔對人, 我覺得依加個新主唱得又唔差喎<br />\n今次專輯第一二主打又幾好聽 , 所以先上嚟推下."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"唱得好好tim 但唔係F.I.R就唔係F.I.R"},{"pid":"42623edb082160a00a5056bea5cf2186a5523931","tid":1143321,"uid":8996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:44:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5f3b5bb98e18a7af78897d3cf587b798e76aa8","tid":1143321,"uid":33293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"聽哂兩首主打歌，兩首都冇Fir 既靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f1e81ecf285b0392800151e3b5a8be7645fd18","tid":1143321,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"我要飛～～～推！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身我唔係 fan，但鍾意聽佢哋比較 popular 嘅歌，<br />\n上個月放假得閒聽返第一張專輯《Lydia》、《我們的愛》，<br />\n手痕一 search，先知原來已經換咗主唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家了解多咗隊 band 分合嘅原因，我會叫自己係 fan <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nF.I.R. (with 新主唱韓睿 Lydia) 同埋 Faye 詹雯婷 solo 兩邊都支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順道 post 之前 post 過三個有關 F.I.R. 換主唱／團名由來嘅 post："},{"pid":"4a0472db192e2a50e82b8647127311c150983d57","tid":1143321,"uid":123308,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"舊年 2018 年 2 月，主唱 Faye 詹雯婷已經離開咗 F.I.R <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年尾 2018 年 10 月，Faye 喺台灣單飛 solo 簽新公司「亞神音樂」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5cLTaV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5cLTaV.jpg&h=673d2264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩個男舊 partners 都有送花籃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJngfqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJngfqb.jpg&h=36336a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n隔日 F.I.R. 剩低嘅兩個（戴黑照嘅陳建寧、結他手阿沁），<br />\n連埋大陸女仔 22 歲嘅韓睿（新主音）喺北京開發佈會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSYbOLf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSYbOLf.jpg&h=7d18619e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFaye 都有送花籃畀對方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcGdhF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcGdhF6.jpg&h=60ea1162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點解會散？<br />\n個人覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">三個原因</span></ins></span>：<br />\n(1) Faye 鍾意的曲風係非商業主流，陳建寧（戴黑超嗰位）同阿沁的就係主流商業曲風<br />\n(2) 陳建寧管／控制得 Faye 太緊<br />\n(3) Faye 2007-10 年同結他手阿沁拍拖，分手結尾，大家面阻阻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">POINT 1</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n其賓 F.I.R. 由 2004 去到 2014，接近 Warner Music Taiwan 份約完結嗰時，<br />\nFaye 已經著手做自己 solo 巡演「小天空」，結他手阿沁都有幫手<br />\n但曲風同陳建寧、阿沁唔同，<br />\nFaye 鍾意的係 EDM (electronic dance music)<br />\n呢一點可以從佢哋兩個男人口中證實<br />\n<ins>(<span style=\"color: blue;\">FIR換主唱事件-陳建寧和阿沁回覆</span> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/QgtCC1DoyC4?t=355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQgtCC1DoyC4%3Ft%3D355&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=95f1a9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QgtCC1DoyC4?t=355</a>)</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更能從 Faye 2018/19 年演繹《Lydia》同埋《我們的愛》時體現出嚟：<br />\n<ins>(<span style=\"color: blue;\">2018.04.25 Faye TTN 小太空 Opening &amp;《Lydia》</span> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/Dm5wFMlB-3Y?t=57\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDm5wFMlB-3Y%3Ft%3D57&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=67453123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Dm5wFMlB-3Y?t=57</a>)</ins><br />\n（Faye 脫離 F.I.R. 後首度來港喺 Live House TTN This Town Needs 表演）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>(<span style=\"color: blue;\">9.29 Faye 飛 賽後演唱《我們的愛》</span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PpRvYacuCXI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPpRvYacuCXI&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b76d43d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PpRvYacuCXI</a>)</ins><br />\n（今年年頭台灣表演）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從以上兩段片睇，即使要翻唱經典作品，Faye 都要用 EDM 版本<br />\n有人可能話係版權問題，但我唔認為係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係版權問題，Faye 應該直頭唔唱得<br />\n<br />\n喺以下呢個台灣專訪，可以睇得出以前 F.I.R. 時期大家一齊好紅好成功，<br />\n但其實 Faye 唔太鍾意呢類商業成功歌曲：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">「青春十年全交給了 F.I.R，真正的夢想仍被壓抑著，發行《小太空》的心態，「其實我覺得有點像是，回到當時第一張專輯（《飛兒樂團》）的初衷再繼續走下去。」她說：「其實很難用團體的方式再繼續走了，因為你 under 在太多商業考量之下的時候，真的很難⋯⋯。但我不是說我們做不好商業這件事情，你可以很有能力的做商業，可是我不是很想要繼續做，我已經三十⋯⋯多了，不想講。」」<br />\n<br />\n「《小太空》巡迴演出，她預計會唱 F.I.R 的歌，並不覺得發了個人專輯就要與團體切割：「我完全沒有在避諱說，如果你從我的個人的音樂裡面，可以聽到某一點 F.I.R 的脈絡或影子的話，那都是很自然的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n只不過她選唱的僅限於真正喜歡的作品：「你知道，第一張專輯有很多我很喜歡的歌，我們一直都沒有在唱。Always 在唱什麼〈你的微笑〉、〈我們的愛〉。我不是不喜歡〈我們的愛〉，我很喜歡這首，但我沒有那麼喜歡〈你的微笑〉。」她語畢大笑，你我明白就很好。<br />\n<br />\n「你知道，我在錄音室裡唱〈你的微笑〉的時候，真的超痛苦的。臉超臭，超生氣的，氣憤。我是用很生氣的態度去唱〈你的微笑〉的！」」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(<a href=\"https://blow.streetvoice.com/34057-%E3%80%90%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E3%80%91-%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E9%A3%9B%EF%BC%9Afaye/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblow.streetvoice.com%2F34057-%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E3%2580%2591-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%25A3%259B%25EF%25BC%259Afaye%2F&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=a6f6c791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blow.streetvoice.com/34057-%E3%80%90%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E3%80%91-%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E9%A3%9B%EF%BC%9Afaye/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">POINT 2</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n呢度可以去到 point 2，陳建寧係背後音樂創作人（例如幫陳奕迅作過《婚禮的祝福》）<br />\n你可以當佢係周星馳（導演），一定要規定其他人點做點做<br />\n同樣道理，樂團上台表演，大家點郁，點企位，幾時對望﹐<br />\n陳建寧都有指示，Faye 一定要跟：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8TwwOXh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8TwwOXh.png&h=5b6190e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(YouTube - 2005.05.09康熙來了完整版(第六季第17集) 兩岸最火團體－F.I.R<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A5pdlPe5H_I?t=266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA5pdlPe5H_I%3Ft%3D266&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=ed6fefbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A5pdlPe5H_I?t=266</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017 年年中，Faye 仲係 F.I.R. 成員時，喺大陸 promote 緊佢嘅 solo album《小太空》，<br />\n接訪專訪時，咁樣評價以前 F.I.R. 時期嘅感覺：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KOGHVCQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKOGHVCQ.png&h=5eb6a804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nKuyhRc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnKuyhRc.png&h=cc5758d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Waaj4z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Waaj4z.png&h=38e4823b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHjBZ4B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHjBZ4B.png&h=9568abd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(YouTube - Faye飞专访：放下过去才能真正飞翔<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vU_ZXCt_bFE?t=28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvU_ZXCt_bFE%3Ft%3D28&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=cdad3e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vU_ZXCt_bFE?t=28</a>)<br />\n<br />\n你諗返 point no. 1，Faye 跟本唔鍾意陳建寧／阿沁曲風，<br />\n但又咁啱走埋一齊，所以做到《Lydia》、《我們的愛》都真係算係奇跡<br />\n成功係靠陳建寧／阿沁背後作曲功力，加上 Faye 的歌喉<br />\n真心唔係單靠邊一個單獨可以成功，一定係要夾埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n但大家音樂風格都唔同，陳建寧聽落又好似咁高壓去管理 F.I.R.，<br />\n自然令 Faye 反感，根本合作唔開心，以致後來 F.I.R. 2013-18 沉寂期，<br />\n唔係真係因為兩個男嘅冇晒靈感創作，而係 <span style=\"color: red;\">Faye 唔肯唱</span>，<br />\n所以 2015 年大陸連續劇《花千骨》主題曲，冇錯係有 F.I.R. 個名，係佢哋（兩個男人）創作，<br />\n但唱的並不是 Faye，而係彭佳慧。原因？就係 Faye 唔肯合作<br />\n<br />\n我唔會話覺得邊個錯，藝術人自然會有執著，你見周星馳後期做導演就知，<br />\n只不過呢啲嘢真係好人夾人，冇話對與錯嘅&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">POINT 3</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n2007 年阿沁同 Faye 拍拖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ieap83P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fieap83P.jpg&h=10821275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿沁甚至喺演唱會求婚，但最後都係唔能夠開花結果，去到 2010 年就散咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8jN60Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8jN60Y.jpg&h=6b5ebb6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2014 年阿沁鍾意咗自己「練習生公司」（類似韓國嗰啲）旗下嘅一個台灣女網紅，<br />\n最後 2015 年結婚，同年亦生咗個女，2017 年生第二個女<br />\n<br />\n正所謂邊度食就唔好喺邊度屙，<br />\n大家分咗手，但大家都要登台出碟搵食，面阻阻都要頂硬上<br />\n然而去到結埋婚生埋女，我相信阿沁老婆都唔會鍾意阿沁日日對住個 ex，<br />\n同時大家都尷尬<br />\n<br />\n集合以上三點，你就知點解 F.I.R. Faye 同兩位男成員分開，其實早有伏綫<br />\n<br />\n唔覺唔覺打咗一大篇嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都係想講，喺 YouTube 上面唔少 comments 都見到好多人都話兩個男人冇用，<br />\n踢走個主音，換過個後生，還我 Faye 云云<br />\n<br />\n但其實佢哋根本唔知道，女主唱阿 Faye 跟本唔鍾意 F.I.R. 成功商業曲風，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2013-18 沉寂期，兩個男叫 Faye 返嚟唱佢哋作嘅作品，又唔肯唱，<br />\n唔鍾意風格，但又唔走，以致 2014-18 幾年冇出過碟</span><br />\n<br />\n大佬，夾 band 嘅嘢，幕後嘅人作好晒，但主唱唔唱唔合作，咁你想點？<br />\n成隊 band 等你一個唱先開到飯，<br />\n而你就可以好不公平咁 under 隊 band 個名單飛，爽歪歪咁出 solo<br />\n所以最後唱片公司整走 Faye 真係無可厚非<br />\n<br />\n大家有興趣可以睇吓百度貼吧嘅 post，<br />\n真心大陸嗰邊理性歌迷分析得幾好，女主唱 Faye 都要負返責任，<br />\n但奈何冇聽開／外人眼中，女仔就通常係被恰嘅一個，以致觀感上好似兩個男錯晒咁款<br />\n簡化字慎入：<br />\n『Better Life』关于 F.I.R. 被迫拆团重组的前因后果<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/6068032048?pn=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F6068032048%3Fpn%3D1&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=67d161fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/6068032048?pn=1</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，只可以講佢哋彼此嘅成功，就好似拍拖咁，<br />\n因誤會而結合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因了解而分開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前的 F.I.R. 只能長存心中，成為回憶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1048bd7ed1523d619288d77a69614671dd07121","tid":1143321,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"FIR換主唱事件-陳建寧和阿沁回覆<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QgtCC1DoyC4?t=345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQgtCC1DoyC4%3Ft%3D345&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=11c0b037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QgtCC1DoyC4?t=345</a><br />\n<br />\n講多少少，其實睇返上面段片大概 5m45s，<br />\n你會見到黑超陳建寧講，佢哋三個內部都曾經傾過，<br />\n諗住用 S.H.E. 嘅 Hebe（田馥甄）發展個 mode 做藍本，<br />\n即係畀前女主音 Faye under 隊 band，但同時可以獨自個人發展，<br />\n鍾意返返嚟個團就返／個團需要佢返嚟就返，<br />\n但 Faye 唔肯，咁注定 Faye 要同陳建寧同阿沁分道揚鑣<br />\n<br />\n真心唔捨得青春回憶嘅 band 分裂到咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但同時理解到真係舊 F.I.R. 分裂呢個事實係不可逆轉<br />\n唯有真心祝福兩邊再闖高峰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外再補充一下，其實 F.I.R. 三個英文字，的確來自 Fairyland in Reality，<br />\n睇返 F.I.R. 第一張同名專輯就知，唔係話轉咗新主唱後先改口作故仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lh8GAk1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLh8GAk1.jpg&h=617db7a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5C4x7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5C4x7J.jpg&h=5e03ac5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三個當初只有 Faye 有英文名，兩個男嘅都係叫「建寧老師」同埋「阿沁」，<br />\n後來唱片公司為求夾返個團名，先叫陳建寧做 Ian，阿沁做 Real，<br />\n所以叫 F.I.R. 並唔係以佢哋三個人個英文名開頭取名，唔似 S.H.E.，唔好倒果為因，<br />\n奈何唔了解背景 (Fairyland in Reality) 嘅人會覺得叫 F.I.R. 係完全因為三個人嘅名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uY9Ofmd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuY9Ofmd.png&h=21b4014e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhpRXzD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhpRXzD.png&h=0dff5003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8k2jN1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8k2jN1.png&h=d7c05f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8m8OZN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8m8OZN3.png&h=1dc26b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(<span style=\"color: blue;\">「飛兒樂團」新女主唱接棒 陳建寧解釋F.I.R.團名意義</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=THNaUEHEnAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTHNaUEHEnAc&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=9eef2066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=THNaUEHEnAc</a>)<br />\n<br />\n更甚嘅係，其實一開頭佢哋係叫 K.I.R. (Kiss in Reality)，<br />\n不過唱片公司唔鍾意，於是先叫做 F.I.R.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3axPKeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3axPKeW.jpg&h=24d93e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRzRXzX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRzRXzX.jpg&h=58afe8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3axG1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3axG1E.jpg&h=0412cbf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ReLhS8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FReLhS8m.jpg&h=d35db542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecgwXz4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecgwXz4.jpg&h=abe3f38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6nV2jOs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6nV2jOs.jpg&h=b4ceae19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtXL11O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtXL11O.jpg&h=149ec5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n部份 source: （簡代字慎入）<br />\n『RE:YOUTH』Fariyland in Reality 团名的由来<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/6092660904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F6092660904&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=548ab521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/6092660904</a>"},{"pid":"e40403ea50f38937c821f64a8d4f22e6833a47d6","tid":1143321,"uid":123308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"講返新主唱，韓睿Lydia 其實真係音域好廣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建寧老師同阿沁揀得佢係真係有原因<br />\n<br />\n呢張第八張專輯第一首我聽嘅歌係《愛上屬於你的天空》<br />\n校到最大聲聽，嘩真係聽到起雞皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果將歌詞代入係陳建寧同阿沁向 Faye 講，更加感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（不過首歌應該係講欺凌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"faa1de8aeff17f066637ef2ea7277db135e25ed9","tid":1143321,"uid":246986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"都係鍾意以前嘅F.I.R<br />\n依家太商業化嘅曲風真係無聽嘅必要"},{"pid":"8ef4c499d480a2a0aa781988e6d65e76c7e54f4d","tid":1143321,"uid":5810,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"新主音個樣辨識度好低，化妝同着衫都好韓流，冇以前飛咁有個人風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d37e44478ab7e9c450da86934b36130da572e59","tid":1143321,"uid":54976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"仲記得佢地好多歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLYDIA,我們的愛,FLY AWAY, 千年之戀, 把愛放開,我要飛, 月牙灣, 讓愛重生,淚光閃爍"},{"pid":"9522dd1e0d86679262f92006aff8682853ad852b","tid":1143321,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:34:54.000Z","msg":"如果大家有上 YouTube 睇 MV 睇埋啲 comments，或者 even 上吓啲大陸論壇，都有一種咁嘅論調，大致有兩點：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(1)</span> 第一張 F.I.R. 同名專輯起點非常高，製作水準極度認真，以致後來自己亦無法超越自己<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(2)</span> 將第一張專輯所有歌打散去往後每張專輯做第一主打，更為可取，可長做長有<br />\n<br />\n題外話，製作認真呢點陳建寧真係唔係講笑，<br />\n出道時期 DEMO 做到成隻真 CD 咁，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8b6MXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8b6MXT.png&h=eb5d46e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XtRiC4u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtRiC4u.png&h=5f05a1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8guj6ZE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8guj6ZE.png&h=2e52f704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHOkRpq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHOkRpq.png&h=39787016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC35h4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC35h4m.png&h=7d9c220b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pp3wX3p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpp3wX3p.png&h=dd397bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYU0Rov.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYU0Rov.png&h=de5d5414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHXUVQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHXUVQe.png&h=de57c8ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohFjnvk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohFjnvk.png&h=0aa960f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUZPKJH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUZPKJH.png&h=1b00aec9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2jK0Rpr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2jK0Rpr.png&h=9c9bdb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMQCTCJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMQCTCJ.png&h=2077f24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWwbdCD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWwbdCD.png&h=49bd1d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbgnkhA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbgnkhA.png&h=6d85a090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZxE6Xw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZxE6Xw.png&h=43ea47c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有非對外公開嘅 F.I.R. 自我介紹雜誌：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WEwdyN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WEwdyN.png&h=d1a08b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rit5h0v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frit5h0v.png&h=520b5a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Vmq2sd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Vmq2sd.png&h=4bee7c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOGq2sh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOGq2sh.png&h=9c6c0151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n（冇計，大陸簡化字網先有（啲 fans cap 低），YouTube 唔見有：）<br />\n20110518F.I.R.佼個朋友吧（Part2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.tudou.com/v/XMTc5OTM0NTg0MA==.html?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.tudou.com%2Fv%2FXMTc5OTM0NTg0MA%3D%3D.html%3F&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=340300c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://video.tudou.com/v/XMTc5OTM0NTg0MA==.html?</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上最流行嘅出道作品《Lydia》同埋《我們的愛》都係喺第一張 F.I.R. 同名專輯入面，<br />\n不過當然後來都有《千年之戀》、《月牙彎》等等經典<br />\n<br />\n個人認為前主唱 Faye 功不可沒，因為係靠佢唱出嚟，<br />\n但背後作曲編曲兩位更加係背後嘅引擎<br />\n<br />\n《Lydia》曲風係古典巴洛克風格 + 抒情搖滾<br />\n《千年之戀》好有東方民族風，好大氣<br />\n《月牙彎》更加係古典 + 現代結合<br />\n<br />\n去到而家第八張專輯《末日青春 : 補完計劃 (Re: Youth)》，<br />\n新歌嘅曲風真係「好 F.I.R.」，印證 F.I.R. 依然係 F.I.R.，冇變過，<br />\n所以即使轉咗主唱，聽多幾次後，會發覺仍然係熟悉嘅 F.I.R.，<br />\n如果你跟開 F.I.R.，呢張新專輯應該好易上腦<br />\n<br />\n至於前主唱 Faye 詹雯婷已經去咗 EDM 電子舞曲世畀，<br />\n大家有聽佢《小太空》album 就知，<br />\n我個人嚟講會話好特別鍾意，但因為係 Faye，所以都會支持"},{"pid":"96897a97efda942347c883e1c553a40ae768b541","tid":1143321,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"上面打錯，但太長廢事 quote：<br />\n<br />\n至於前主唱 Faye 詹雯婷已經去咗 EDM 電子舞曲世畀，<br />\n大家有聽佢《小太空》album 就知，<br />\n我個人嚟講<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>會話好特別鍾意，但因為係 Faye，所以都會支持"},{"pid":"7edf75a03bcdbdd1a727e07af55f6d153f8520f7","tid":1143321,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gi