ike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"希望大家支持新嘅F.I.R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"難得有同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面都講咗好多，<br />\n建寧老師同阿沁唔係冇試過，<br />\n已經多次請 Faye 返嚟唱，<br />\n但 Faye 拒絕，唔要既單飛又可合體嘅模式，<br />\n要完全獨立單飛做佢 EDM style 嘅音樂，<br />\n以致最後被唱片公司移除，分道揚鑣<br />\n我兩邊都支持，尊重兩種風格<br />\n<br />\n當然呢度梗係支持建寧老師同阿沁嘅歌 + 詞以新主唱韓睿 Lydia 唱出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}